Additions to the Encyrtidae and Mymaridae (Chalcidoidea) of India with new distribution and host records for some speciesEncyrtidae and Mymaridae of India have not been surveyed in depth and hosts are not known for most of the species as the methods of collections used are passive and do not yield firsthand information on the hosts. Based on our ongoing surveys on the Encyrtidae and Mymaridae of India, we report here new distribution and host records for some species.